get the modified author "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
=======================================================================

NAME
----

get the modified author - Retrieve the author who last edited the current post.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Retrieve the author who last edited the current post.

USAGE
-----

` <?php echo get_the_modified_author(); ?> `

RETURN VALUES
-------------

 `(string)` 
:   The author's display name.

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`get_the_modified_author()` is located in
`wp-includes/author-template.php`.

